Apportez-le-moi !

124
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:47,220
Cependant,

125
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:48,260
Khan.

126
00:08:48,590 --> 00:08:50,300
Ce sont des mercenaires de Tocharian.

127
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,390
Ils...

128
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,890
Ce sont les plus forts du désert.

129
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:56,180
Centrale de conneries !

130
