134
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:07,050
Battons-nous ensemble.

135
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:09,180
Nous allons les écraser aussi !

136
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,430
Charge!

137
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,390
C'est l'ordre de Khan.

138
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,970
Prenez vos armes.

139
